Name: team_size
Description: Number of workers assigned to a team

Name: sprint_length_days
Description: The duration of a single sprint in days

Name: worker_assign_sprint
Description: Assign a specific worker to a specific sprint

Name: feature_priority
Description: Priority level assigned to a feature

Name: story_points
Description: Number of story points assigned to a user story

Name: task_sequence
Description: The order in which tasks are processed

Name: resource_allocation_budget
Description: Budget allocated to a specific feature or sprint

Name: skill_requirement_threshold
Description: Minimum skill level required for a task

Name: contingency_buffer_days
Description: Buffer time added to a task or sprint for uncertainty

Name: max_concurrent_tasks
Description: Maximum number of tasks a worker can handle simultaneously
